verses.text: \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w*, \w my|strong="H3068"\w* heart \w is|strong="H3068"\w* not exalted: nor \w are|strong="H3068"\w* \w my|strong="H3068"\w* eyes lofty. Neither \w have|strong="H3068"\w* \w I|strong="H3068"\w* walked \w in|strong="H3068"\w* great matters, nor \w in|strong="H3068"\w* wonderful things above \w me|strong="H7121"\w*.

\w If|strong="H1961"\w* \w I|strong="H8085"\w* \w was|strong="H1961"\w* \w not|strong="H1961"\w* humbly minded, \w but|strong="H1961"\w* exalted \w my|strong="H8085"\w* soul: \w As|strong="H1961"\w* \w a|strong="H1961"\w* child \w that|strong="H8085"\w* \w is|strong="H6963"\w* weaned \w is|strong="H6963"\w* towards \w his|strong="H8085"\w* mother, \w so|strong="H1961"\w* reward \w in|strong="H8085"\w* \w my|strong="H8085"\w* soul.

Let \w Israel|strong="H8104"\w* hope \w in|strong="H5975"\w* \w the|strong="H0518"\w* \w Lord|strong="H0136"\w*, \w from|strong="H8104"\w* henceforth now \w and|strong="H5975"\w* \w for|strong="H0518"\w* \w ever|strong="H4310"\w*.
